Package controller

Package that acts as the controller for the data flow between database to model object.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AutoGroupServlet
    A servlet that manages inputs from automaticGroupDetection and results from AutoGroupDAO.
    HeatMapServlet
    A servlet that manages inputs from heatmapPage and results from HeatMapDAO.
    LoginServlet
    A servlet that manages inputs from index and results from UserDAO.
    LogoutServlet
    A servlet that logouts the user.
    ReportServlet
    A servlet that manages inputs from basicReport, topKPopularPlaces, topKCompanions, topKNextPlaces and results from ReportDAO.
    UpdateServlet
    A servlet that manages inputs from bootstrapUpdate and results from UploadDAO.
    UploadServlet
    A servlet that manages inputs from bootstrapInitialize and results from UploadDAO.

Package controller Description

Package that acts as the controller for the data flow between database to model object. Also in charge of updating the view whenever data changes.
